    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a mirror-like finish, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or any visible imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of bolster wear, while the original floor mats look untouched. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. it has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive folder of service records included. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body panels. It rides on a fresh set of premium tires and recently underwent a full preventative fluid service. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Included in the sale are both original master keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner's manuals.",
